Notes: Game was tied 18-18 in first half when SP went on 11-1 run...LC cut lead to
36-33 in second half when SP went on 16-0 run...After a LC basket, SP scored
next nine points for 61-35 lead...SP's Nechuta had one three-pointer all year
and hit two three-pointers during 16-0 run.
Game.Officials: Tom Kissinger,  Terry Erickson,  Michelle Miller
